des:
Wedding Planner when live will allow you to set multiple countdowns with appointments and reminders. When fully released you will be able to say the following commands:

Alexa, What are my countdowns?
Alexa, What are my reminders?
Alexa, What are my appointments?
Alexa, What is left on my checklists?
Alexa, Call Jeweler
Alexa, Call Travel Agent
Alexa, Add this to checklist
Alexa, New Countdown
Alexa, New Reminder
Alexa, New Appointment

Thank you for visiting Wedding Planner demo! We hope your wedding is perfect! We hope you visit our sponsors and leave us and them your valuable feedback! Please check out our other products in the Alexa App and at bubblelogix.com! Wedding Planner is a Bubble Logix property designed on voice flow!
